<b>2013 May 20&nbsp;&nbsp;    Master class with Saburo Takayasu Shihan<br>
2013 May 21&nbsp;&nbsp;    Open class with Saburo Takayasu Shihan
</b><br><br><br>

Saburo Takayasu Shihan, 7th dan, from Sydney, Australia will be giving a 2-1/2 hour master class on Monday 2013 May 20. Session is at MAC's Makati Sports Club dojo, starting at 1830 hrs sharp. Participants must be 2nd kyu or higher. All qualified aikidoists are welcome.<br><br>

Takayasu Shihan will then conduct an open class on Tuesday, May 21st, at the same venue. All ranks are welcome at this class. All interested aikidoists are welcome.<br>


